<p><strong>Background:</strong><br />
John Ehrett serves as Legal Counsel for Senator Josh Hawley. In this role, he provides legal advice and support on legislative and policy matters, helping to draft legislation, analyze legal issues, and advise the Senator on a range of policy topics. Ehrett has a background in law and public policy with experience in legal analysis and legislative affairs. He holds a JD from Yale Law School and a BA from Patrick Henry College.</p>

